to run the program from an inputfile, simply type:
$ make
and then type:
$ ./prodcon [arg] [arg] <inputfile
-----------------------------------------------------
to run the program from the command line, simply type:
$ make
and then type:
$ ./prodcon [arg] [arg]
then type all of your commands separated by the Enter key
for example:
$ T1
$ S1
$ T2
$ T4
then use the command Ctrl-D to signify the end of your arg inputs.
------------------------------------------------------

